org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.tests.lang

Class InListMultiProbeTest.DataRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.tests.lang.InListMultiProbeTest.DataRow
  • Enclosing class:
    InListMultiProbeTest

    private static class InListMultiProbeTest.DataRow
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class: An instance of DataRow represents a single row in DATA_TABLE. We use this class to store in-memory versions of the rows, which are helpful for inserting the rows and for checking query results.
